<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FitCalc | TDEE Calculator & Nutrition Guide</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script defer src="script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container nav-content">
            <a href="#home" class="logo">Fit<span>Calc</span></a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#intro">What is TDEE?</a></li>
                <li><a href="#calculator">Calculator</a></li>
                <li><a href="#diet">Diet Guide</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="hamburger"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Master Your Metabolism</h1>
                <p>Calculate your daily calorie needs and unlock your fitness potential with precision.</p>
                <a href="#calculator" class="btn-primary">Calculate Your TDEE</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- TDEE Introduction Page -->
    <section id="intro" class="section container">
        <div class="text-content">
            <h2>Understanding TDEE</h2>
            <p><strong>TDEE</strong> stands for Total Daily Energy Expenditure. It is an estimation of how many calories you burn per day when exercise is taken into account. It is calculated by first figuring out your Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR), then multiplying that value by an activity multiplier.</p>
            <div class="grid-3">
                <div class="card"><h3>BMR</h3><p>Energy used at complete rest for vital functions.</p></div>
                <div class="card"><h3>TEF</h3><p>Calories burned while digesting food.</p></div>
                <div class="card"><h3>NEAT</h3><p>Energy used for non-exercise movement like walking.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Calculator Page -->
    <section id="calculator" class="section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="center">TDEE Calculator</h2>
            <div class="calc-wrapper">
                <form id="tdee-form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Gender</label>
                        <select id="gender"><option value="male">Male</option><option value="female">Female</option></select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Age</label>
                        <input type="number" id="age" placeholder="e.g. 25" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Weight (kg)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="weight" placeholder="e.g. 70" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Height (cm)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="height" placeholder="e.g. 175" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Activity Level</label>
                        <select id="activity">
                            <option value="1.2">Sedentary (Office job)</option>
                            <option value="1.375">Lightly Active (1-2 days/week)</option>
                            <option value="1.55">Moderately Active (3-5 days/week)</option>
                            <option value="1.725">Very Active (6-7 days/week)</option>
                            <option value="1.9">Extra Active (Physical Job)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Calculate</button>
                </form>
                <div id="results" class="results-box hidden">
                    <h3>Your Daily Maintenance Calories:</h3>
                    <div class="result-value"><span id="tdee-output">0</span> kcal</div>
                    <p>To lose weight, aim for ~<span id="loss-output">0</span> kcal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Diet Information Page -->
    <section id="diet" class="section container">
        <h2>Diet & Nutrition Guide</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3>Macronutrient Split</h3>
                <p>Once you know your calories, focus on macros:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Protein:</strong> 1.8g - 2.2g per kg of body weight for muscle retention.</li>
                    <li><strong>Fats:</strong> 20-30% of total calories for hormonal health.</li>
                    <li><strong>Carbs:</strong> The remainder of your calories for energy.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h3>Quick Tip</h3>
                <p>Consistency is more important than perfection. A 500-calorie daily deficit usually results in 0.5kg of fat loss per week.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container center">
            <p>&copy; 2024 FitCalc. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:support@fitcalc.com">support@fitcalc.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
